<sentence><TIMEX3 definite="FALSE" tid="t13" type="DATE" value="2002-11" valueFromSurface="XXXX-11">昨年１１月</TIMEX3>、Ｊ１復帰を<event class="" eid="e67">決め</event>、声援に<event class="" eid="e68">応える</event>セ大阪。</sentence>
